  "comment": "The Force 7 LED Leko from BB&S Lighting is a brilliant combination of high light output\nand great color rendering.\nFORCE 7 Features:\n• CRI / TLCI 97+\n• 185W draw from 48VDC power supply\n• True 8/16 bit flicker free internal dimmer\n• Power-saving long life LED single source\n• No hot spots with even edge to edge light\n• Excellent shadow rendering, no double shadows with Gobo or effects\n• Crisp Gobo projection\n• Clean straight cut with beam shapers\n• Ultra silent operation, quietest fan in the industry\n• Completely smooth full range dimming from 0-100%\n• High speed adjustable strobe\n• DMX 512/RDM in/out\n• Ideal for filmmaking, broadcasting, studios, architectural, museums\nand other entertainment lighting",
